The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 47

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

Scotty reveals the scores for the master bedrooms and ensuites and there's just half a point between first and second place. The teams need to finish the exterior terraces and they'll also receive $5000 to fix up their worst room.
